data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! BEAUTIFUL 1 BED-1 BATH -1 CAR GARAGE IN THE DESIRABLE COMMUNITY OF HUNTINGTON LANDMARK. THIS FABULOUS CONDO FEATURES, VAULTED CEILINGS, OPEN FLOOR PLAN, NEW APPLIANCES, FRESH PAINT, LARGE MASTER BEDROOM CLOSET, LAUNDRY CLOSET IN THE PATIO WITH WASHER AND DRYER INCLUDED AND LOTS OF PARKING RIGHT IN FRONT OF THE CONDO.  ENJOY THE OCEAN BREEZE IN THE SPACIOUS  PATIO. THE COMMUNITY OFFERS RESORT STYLE LIVING WITH THE MANY AMENITIES, 2 HEATED SWIMMING POOLS AND SPA, PICKLE BALL AND TENNIS COURTS, PUTTING GREEN, SHUFFLE BOARD, GYM AND WEIGHT ROOM, CLUB HOUSE, GATED AND GUARDED COMMUNITY, CERAMIC ROOM, WOOD-SHOP, LIBRARY, BILLIARD ROOM, AND MANY ACTIVITIES FOR YOUR ENJOYMENT.
